<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="95" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="2.[843,1494,554,998]" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">
Two specimens collected by Malme were used by Fries to describe and illustrate 
<taxonomicName authorityName="R. E. Fr. In" authorityYear="2014" box="[1090,1203,586,610]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Bombax" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="elegans">
<emphasis box="[1090,1203,586,610]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">B. elegans</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation author="FRIES" box="[1219,1427,586,610]" firstAuthor="FRIES" page="27 - 28" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" pagination="27 - 28" refId="ref6547" refString="FRIES, R. E. (1908). Studien uber die amerikanische Columniferenflora; Fam. Bombaceae. Kongl. Svenska Vetensk. Acad. Handl. 42 (12): 27 - 28." type="journal article" year="1908">FRIES, 1908: 27-28</bibRefCitation>
, plate IV) and thus they are 
<typeStatus box="[1082,1178,619,643]" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">syntypes</typeStatus>
of this name. The collection dated 
<date box="[908,1025,651,675]" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" value="1903-07-04">4.VII.1903</date>
[SR11279] has several, separate floral buds and juvenile flowers, and the collections dated from 
<date box="[1381,1494,683,707]" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" value="1902-12-04">4.XII.1902</date>
have mature, seven-foliolate leaves ([SR11280], [S10-38650]). 
<bibRefCitation author="ROBYNS" box="[843,1049,748,772]" firstAuthor="ROBYNS" page="59" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" pagination="1 - 315" refId="ref6833" refString="ROBYNS, A. (1963). Essai de monographie du genre Bombax s. l. (Bombacaceae). Bull. Jard. Bot. Etat Bruxelles 33: 1 - 315." type="journal article" year="1963">ROBYNS (1963: 59)</bibRefCitation>
considered both vegetative and reproductive specimens as type material of 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">
<taxonomicName authorityName="R. E. Fr. In" authorityYear="2014" box="[1235,1352,780,804]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Bombax" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="elegans">B. elegans</taxonomicName>
: “ 
<date box="[1387,1486,780,804]" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" value="1903-07">jul. 1903</date>
, Malme s.n. (f., fl.; 
<typeStatus box="[1046,1151,812,836]" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">holotypus</typeStatus>
<taxonomicName authorityName="R. E. Fr. In" authorityYear="2014" box="[1158,1271,812,836]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Bombax" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="elegans">B. elegans</taxonomicName>
S)”,
</emphasis>
but he failed to designate a 
<typeStatus box="[969,1067,845,869]" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">lectotype</typeStatus>
for this name. We designate the flowering specimen as the 
<typeStatus box="[1069,1171,877,901]" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">lectotype</typeStatus>
for 
<taxonomicName authorityName="R. E. Fr. In" authorityYear="2014" box="[1217,1332,877,901]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Bombax" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="elegans">
<emphasis box="[1217,1332,877,901]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">B. elegans</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
based on both Fries’ indication of new species status 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">
“ 
<taxonomicName authority="R. E. Fr." authorityName="R. E. Fr. In" authorityYear="2014" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Bombax" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="elegans" status="n. sp.">Bombax elegans R. E. Fr.</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[880,937,942,966]" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
”
</emphasis>
as well as indication of the habitat 
<emphasis box="[1324,1494,942,966]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">(“In cerrados”)</emphasis>
on the specimen label that match Fries’ protologue.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[843,1494,1014,1167]" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">
Since the present 
<typeStatus box="[1073,1172,1014,1038]" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">lectotype</typeStatus>
lacks leaves, which represent diagnostic characters for 
<taxonomicName authority="RIES, 1908: 27 - 28" authorityName="RIES" authorityPageNumber="27 - 28" authorityYear="1908" box="[1112,1362,1046,1070]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Bombax" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="elegans">
<emphasis box="[1112,1222,1046,1070]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">B. elegans</emphasis>
RIES, 1908
</taxonomicName>
: 27-28), we designate the specimen [
<specimenCode box="[1104,1220,1078,1102]" collectionCode="S" country="Sweden" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15668" name="Department of Botany, Swedish Museum of Natural History" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" type="Herbarium">S10-38650</specimenCode>
] as an epitype to permit a precise application of the name in accordance with Art. 9.8 (ICBN-Melbourne).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[843,1493,1183,1239]" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">
The 
<typeStatus box="[930,1028,1183,1207]" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">lectotype</typeStatus>
and epitype of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="RIES" authorityYear="1908" box="[1194,1304,1183,1207]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Bombax" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="elegans">
<emphasis box="[1194,1304,1183,1207]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">B. elegans</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are also 
<typeStatus box="[1400,1493,1183,1207]" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">syntypes</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName authorityName=", HASSLER" authorityYear="1910" box="[872,1220,1215,1239]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Bombax" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="longiflorum" variety="emarginatum">
<emphasis box="[872,1028,1215,1239]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">B. longiflorum</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis box="[1079,1220,1215,1239]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">emarginatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis box="[1221,1228,1215,1239]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
